I give you something.

02:04.792 --> 02:05.792
- What's your game?

02:07.586 --> 02:08.878
- I ain't got no game.

02:12.633 --> 02:14.301
Just wanna give
this to the church.

02:17.555 --> 02:18.764
- What do you get out of it?

02:24.562 --> 02:26.480
- I want you to
cover me in prayer.

02:31.360 --> 02:32.736
That's it.

02:32.820 --> 02:34.530
- That's all you want?

02:34.613 --> 02:35.613
To be covered in prayer?

02:35.656 --> 02:36.699
- That's it, that's all.

02:38.409 --> 02:39.952
I want you to
cover me in prayer.

02:41.912 --> 02:43.289
Sinners need prayer, too.

03:01.599 --> 03:03.392
Bow my head, I close my eyes,

03:03.475 --> 03:06.645
you put your hand on my
shoulder or somethin', what?

03:06.729 --> 03:07.980
Come on, let's go.

03:08.063 --> 03:09.440
- You wanna be covered?

03:10.691 --> 03:11.811
- Yeah, that's right.

03:16.697 --> 03:18.157
- Cover yourself.

03:18.240 --> 03:19.240
- What?

03:20.200 --> 03:24.705
