03:36.008 --> 03:37.635
- Take care, Silk.

03:37.718 --> 03:39.404
- You know, I love what
you did with the place,

03:39.428 --> 03:40.679
you know what I'm sayin'?

03:40.763 --> 03:41.764
It's kinda cool.

03:42.598 --> 03:44.266
I like the car, too.

03:46.685 --> 03:48.896
You should come work for me.

