put a thousand dollars

03:51.398 --> 03:53.442
in your pocket a
week, even more.

03:54.735 --> 03:56.320
Yeah, even more.

03:57.154 --> 03:58.364
This place needs it.

03:58.447 --> 03:59.549
- You know I don't do that.

03:59.573 --> 04:00.449
- I love the minivan.

04:00.532 --> 04:01.700
It looks good on you, too.

04:03.410 --> 04:04.410
Reliable.

04:05.329 --> 04:06.329
Safe.

04:06.956 --> 04:07.956
Economic.

05:23.574 --> 05:24.574
- Hey baby.

05:31.707 --> 05:34.043
I went to the church again.

05:40.799 --> 05:41.799
I'm not ready.

05:47.389 --> 05:49.433
You know, L.J. and Sandra
keep trying to get me

05:49.516 --> 05:50.809
to go up in there, but...

05:54.688 --> 05:56.065
