06:05.532 --> 06:06.885
You know I was
thinking the other day,

06:06.909 --> 06:08.229
maybe I should sit
down and write.

06:09.870 --> 06:11.306
I been talking to
these different people

06:11.330 --> 06:12.456
about survivor's guilt.

06:14.875 --> 06:16.251
So many folks out there.

06:17.503 --> 06:19.713
I won't light it,
I won't light it.

06:32.768 --> 06:33.811
I see you in my dreams.

06:37.773 --> 06:38.857
Baby is alive.

06:39.983 --> 06:41.360
The three of us are happy.

06:49.535 --> 06:50.953
- God, God, yessir, yessir.

06:53.247 --> 06:54.647
Let me tell you
something, Preacher.

06:55.582 --> 06:57.876
You sure enough preached
that thing today, boy.

06:57.960 --> 07:00.254
- They um, they
really seemed like

07:00.337 --> 07:01.588
they was into it today.

07:01.672 --> 07:02.798
- Amen, amen.

07:05.008 --> 07:05.676
- Praise God.

07:05.759 --> 07:06.510
- Hey.

07:06.593 --> 07:07.593
Monies for the day.

07:16.854 --> 07:18.021
- A whole $120?

07:18.105 --> 07:19.982
- Yeah, the whole $120.

07:21.441 --> 07:22.961
Look here, don't go spending
that all in one place.

07:22.985 --> 07:24.185
- Where I'm gonna spend it at?

07:25.028 --> 07:26.028
$120.

07:27.990 --> 07:30.325
- Well, you know you
can give it back to me.

07:30.409 --> 07:31.994
- Don't you play with
the Lord's money.

07:34.246 --> 07:35.246
- Man.

07:38.667 --> 07:40.961
Well, how's everything
going out there?

07:41.044 --> 07:42.254
- Everything's good, man.

07:42.337 --> 07:45.674
Well, you heard
the organ, right?

07:45.757 --> 07:46.860
- Yeah, I wanted to
ask you about that,

07:46.884 --> 07:48.319
'cause it sound like
an old dyin' cat.

07:48.343 --> 07:49.343
- Yeah.

07:50.429 --> 07:54.057
A dying cat that died twice.

07:54.141 --> 07:54.975
- Ooh.

07:55.058 --> 07:55.893
What's going on with it?

07:55.976 --> 07:56.810
- Yeah that thing's dead.

07:56.894 --> 07:58.437
The organ is gone, it's dead.

07:58.520 --> 08:00.647
Yeah, we gonna need a new
one of those, for sure,

08:00.731 --> 08:01.958
but if we don't increase
our tithes and offering,

08:01.982 --> 08:05.444
I mean, we might have to
shut down our pantry box...

08:05.527 --> 08:06.445
- No, no, no.

08:06.528 --> 08:07.839
Lavar, we can't do that
because if we do that,

08:07.863 --> 08:09.423
then the summer camp's
gonna suffer man.

08:09.489 --> 08:10.532
- I know, I know.

08:10.616 --> 08:12.034
