to that event.

08:16.038 --> 08:17.873
- We gonna need
that miracle soon.

08:17.956 --> 08:18.956
- Indeed.

08:21.043 --> 08:23.253
- But is there any good news?

08:23.337 --> 08:24.504
- Yeah, yeah.

