people this morning.

08:28.467 --> 08:30.385
- Your work, praise God.

08:32.011 --> 08:35.474
Now, next time, you might
wanna lead with that.

08:35.557 --> 08:36.475
- With that one?

08:36.558 --> 08:37.308
- Yeah, with that one, right.

08:37.392 --> 08:38.309
- I got you.

08:38.393 --> 08:39.102
- With that particular one.

08:39.186 --> 08:40.062
- Gotcha, copy, copy.

08:40.145 --> 08:40.979
- Bring the confidence up.

08:41.063 --> 08:42.222
- I understand, I understand.

08:42.272 --> 08:43.148
