08:43.232 --> 08:44.399
- Alright.

08:44.483 --> 08:45.752
- Look here man, I'm gonna
get up on outta here.

08:45.776 --> 08:46.985
- Go on, go ahead, alright.

08:47.069 --> 08:48.362
- Alright, mother?

08:48.445 --> 08:49.923
