over to Mother Carey's, okay?

08:49.947 --> 08:51.007
- No, no, you ain't
gotta worry about it.

08:51.031 --> 08:51.740
I'll take it over there.

08:51.823 --> 08:52.532
- You sure?

08:52.616 --> 08:53.283
- Yeah, I'm sure.

08:53.367 --> 08:54.201
- You don't mind?

08:54.284 --> 08:55.452
- No, I'm good, go ahead.

08:55.535 --> 08:56.411
- Alright, see ya tomorrow.

08:56.495 --> 08:57.704
- See ya tomorrow.

08:57.788 --> 08:59.831
