things, so many things.

09:08.382 --> 09:09.716
- He's still working with me.

09:11.009 --> 09:12.928
- Get on outta here.

09:13.011 --> 09:14.011
- Hey, Pastor.

09:15.013 --> 09:15.889
Let me hold something.

09:15.973 --> 09:17.724
- Get out.

09:17.808 --> 09:18.976
Get out, get out.

09:21.228 --> 09:21.937
- See ya tomorrow, man.

09:22.020 --> 09:23.021
- Go on, Levar.

09:34.116 --> 09:35.510
