Social Security.

09:50.215 --> 09:51.455
They make these things so hard.

09:51.508 --> 09:53.677
- Well, you might wanna
clean out your purse.

09:53.760 --> 09:56.305
- Well, so how much is it?

09:56.388 --> 09:57.014
How much do I owe you?

09:57.097 --> 09:59.474
- I thought you said
you forgot your glasses?

09:59.558 --> 10:02.060
- You know how forgetful I am.

10:03.186 --> 10:04.604
