care package here.

10:39.222 --> 10:40.140
- Come on in.

10:40.223 --> 10:40.891
- Alright.

10:40.974 --> 10:41.975
- Have some lemonade.

10:42.059 --> 10:43.060
- That sounds good.

10:43.143 --> 10:44.143
Alright.

10:48.648 --> 10:50.400
Close the door here.

10:50.484 --> 10:52.235
- Yeah, you come on in here.

10:52.319 --> 10:53.653
I'll tell you what.

10:53.737 --> 10:55.030
- Yes ma'am.

10:55.113 --> 10:57.491
- I'm gonna pour you a nice,
tall glass of lemonade.

10:57.574 --> 10:58.992
- Ooh, that sounds good.

10:59.076 --> 11:00.118
It's hot out there.

11:00.202 --> 11:01.220
- It is hot out there.

11:01.244 --> 11:02.287
- Yes ma'am.

11:02.371 --> 11:03.639
I'm gonna go ahead and put
this up for you, alright?

11:03.663 --> 11:04.581
- Alright now.

11:04.664 --> 11:05.874
- Alright.

11:05.957 --> 11:07.677
Gonna make sure that
you are good and you...

11:12.172 --> 11:14.257
- I know.

11:15.175 --> 11:16.426
- That's alright.

11:16.510 --> 11:18.929
- I'll be glad when
the season change

11:19.012 --> 11:20.889
and we get a little
relief from this...

11:20.972 --> 11:22.557
- Well, it cooled
down a little bit.

11:22.641 --> 11:24.101
- Heat now.

11:24.184 --> 11:25.936
- But I wanted to make
sure I saw you before

11:26.019 --> 11:28.980
I went home for the night,

11:29.064 --> 11:30.690
just make sure
everything was alright.

11:34.945 --> 11:36.446
That's some good lemonade.

11:36.530 --> 11:37.406
- Thank you.

11:37.489 --> 11:38.573
- That's good.

11:38.657 --> 11:39.866
- Let me see.

11:39.950 --> 11:41.451
- That is good, Mama Carey.

11:43.078 --> 11:47.165
- Well, little bit too
much lemon for my taste.

11:47.249 --> 11:49.709
- Too much lemon
in it for your taste?

11:50.627 --> 11:52.087
- I can do better than this.

11:53.130 --> 11:55.048
- Well, I'll tell you what.

11:55.132 --> 11:57.134
I'm going back to the
church, get you another box

11:57.217 --> 12:00.679
and then we can have some
more lemonade when I get back.

12:01.847 --> 12:02.722
- Okay.

12:02.806 --> 12:03.974
- Yes ma'am.

12:04.057 --> 12:05.600
And while you gone,
I'm gonna make us

12:05.684 --> 12:06.935
another batch of lemonade.

12:07.018 --> 12:08.246
- Alright,
that sound like a plan.

12:08.270 --> 12:09.479
- Alright.

12:09.563 --> 12:10.957
- Alright, I'll
see you in a minute, alright?

12:10.981 --> 12:12.125
- Alright, darling, thank you.

12:12.149 --> 12:13.149
- Alright.

12:17.028 --> 12:20.157
- I'm gonna throw a couple
of samples in here for you,

12:21.283 --> 12:24.077
if I can grab it,
alright, there we go.

12:24.161 --> 12:25.954
And we have a
shipment every week,

12:26.037 --> 12:28.248
so come back and we will
get you all fixed up.

12:28.331 --> 12:29.207
- That sounds wonderful.

12:29.291 --> 12:30.000
Thank you so much.

12:30.083 --> 12:31.251
- You're welcome.

12:31.334 --> 12:32.645
Thank you for shopping at the.

12:32.669 --> 12:33.688
- Thank you, have a great day.

12:33.712 --> 12:34.712
- Bye, you too.

12:35.755 --> 12:37.466
Thank you.

12:37.549 --> 12:39.009
- Girl another sale?

12:39.092 --> 12:40.802
You are on fire.

12:40.886 --> 12:42.262
This just might work.

12:42.345 --> 12:43.430
- Yes, I'm feeling it.

12:43.513 --> 12:44.657
