it's working for ya.

14:10.100 --> 14:11.309
- Yeah, wanna beer?

14:11.393 --> 14:12.644
- Yes, yes I do.

14:14.145 --> 14:17.315
- So I got tickets to the
show tonight, four tickets.

14:19.818 --> 14:21.444
