- Buy a new organ, alright?

19:15.572 --> 19:18.575
And then take whatever's
left, put half of it

19:18.658 --> 19:20.451
it the pantry and the other half

19:20.535 --> 19:22.078
on the summer camp
program, alright?

19:22.161 --> 19:23.246
Just take care of it.

