21:05.890 --> 21:06.599
- Hey, sweet, we lucked out.

21:06.683 --> 21:07.558
It's a good table?

21:07.642 --> 21:09.852
- Yeah, it is, it's really good.

21:09.936 --> 21:11.062
- So you know what?

21:11.145 --> 21:12.480
It's time for a offering now.

21:12.563 --> 21:13.624
- Sheila, you ever
been here before?

21:13.648 --> 21:14.848
- I haven't but Sandra told me

21:14.899 --> 21:16.818
that the crab cakes
are off the chain.

21:19.278 --> 21:22.156
- They are, but I have
to stay away from shellfish.

21:22.240 --> 21:23.616
- Since when?

21:23.700 --> 21:25.052
- You don't remember
your conference?

