22:00.695 --> 22:02.613
- What is wrong?

22:02.697 --> 22:03.698
- I'm okay, I'm okay.

22:03.781 --> 22:05.450
It's just, all this
stuff that's going on

22:05.533 --> 22:08.494
with my mama, and I
just don't need him

22:08.578 --> 22:09.787
adding on to...

22:09.871 --> 22:11.664
