gonna hear from Sherel Riley.

23:56.769 --> 24:00.356
- So, Sheila,
did you enjoy the show?

24:00.439 --> 24:02.275
- I did.

24:02.358 --> 24:05.903
Good music, good
food, good company.

24:05.987 --> 24:07.947
- Well did you enjoy the show?

24:08.030 --> 24:10.449
- Absolutely, you
know I love Jones.

24:10.533 --> 24:11.951
Got all his albums.

24:12.034 --> 24:12.869
- Me too.

24:12.952 --> 24:14.704
- Ooh, they got
something in common.

24:14.787 --> 24:15.538
Look at that.

24:15.621 --> 24:16.789
- That's right honey.

24:16.873 --> 24:18.058
I'm sorry, you'll have
to excuse my wife.

24:18.082 --> 24:21.878
She was a cupid or
something in a past life.

24:21.961 --> 24:23.171
- You know what?

24:23.254 --> 24:25.673
My mom would try to
fix me up for years,

24:25.756 --> 24:26.799
so I'm used to it, so...

24:26.883 --> 24:27.717
- Yeah?

24:27.800 --> 24:29.093
- Really, alright.

24:31.012 --> 24:32.513
- Do you guys want a lift?

24:32.597 --> 24:33.806
- No, I'm taking a cab.

24:33.890 --> 24:35.349
- Yeah, I Ubered here, so...

24:35.433 --> 24:37.894
- Well maybe you guys
can take a car together.

24:37.977 --> 24:39.520
Uber together.

24:42.023 --> 24:43.524
- Okay.

24:46.652 --> 24:47.862
- Yeah, I'll call.

24:52.950 --> 24:55.786
- don't you ever
disrespect me in public again.

24:55.870 --> 24:57.705
- But baby, you told me to st...

24:57.788 --> 24:58.868
- I don't care what I said.

24:58.915 --> 24:59.624
- Well, I...

24:59.707 --> 25:00.416
- I do what I wanna do.

25:00.499 --> 25:01.500
- Okay, okay, okay.

25:01.584 --> 25:02.853
I understand, but that was
money for the grocery bill.

25:02.877 --> 25:03.711
- You get paid Friday.

25:03.794 --> 25:05.213
- But I am not the bank!

25:07.215 --> 25:08.049
- I am gonna...

25:08.132 --> 25:08.966
I don't care what you do.

25:09.050 --> 25:09.717
You know what?

25:09.800 --> 25:11.010
I'll tell you what.

25:11.093 --> 25:12.362
- Take your hands off her.

25:13.137 --> 25:15.223
Take your hands off her.

25:15.306 --> 25:17.266
- My God, no wait, please.

25:17.350 --> 25:20.603
He's having a heart attack,
please call the police!

25:20.686 --> 25:21.938
Help!

25:22.021 --> 25:24.357
- So, nothing happened?

25:25.816 --> 25:27.526
- No, nothing.

25:28.611 --> 25:30.863
Why do you sound
so disappointed?

25:30.947 --> 25:32.549
- I mean, I woulda
thought you'd get like,

25:32.573 --> 25:34.075
a kiss on the
cheek or something.

25:34.158 --> 25:35.826
- I know, that would
have been kinda nice.

25:35.910 --> 25:36.619
- You see?

25:36.702 --> 25:38.079
Thank you.

25:38.162 --> 25:40.957
So, when are you
two going out again?

25:41.040 --> 25:42.750
- I don't know.

25:42.833 --> 25:45.294
I haven't talked to him, at all.

25:45.378 --> 25:46.712
- He hasn't called you?

25:46.796 --> 25:47.796
- No.

25:48.965 --> 25:50.800
- Okay, have you called him?

25:50.883 --> 25:52.969
- I tried, but he didn't answer.

25:53.803 --> 25:56.013
- Okay, okay, alright.

25:57.139 --> 25:58.224
You're gonna go over there.

25:58.307 --> 25:59.058
- What?

25:59.141 --> 26:00.351
- Yep.

26:00.434 --> 26:02.037
- That is gonna make
me look so desperate.

26:02.061 --> 26:03.061
- But you are.

26:03.104 --> 26:04.647
- You are not right!

26:05.648 --> 26:06.315
- I'm kidding, I'm kidding.

26:06.399 --> 26:07.066
Sheila, I'm kidding.

26:07.149 --> 26:08.651
It's a joke, okay?

26:08.734 --> 26:10.403
But seriously, alright.

26:10.486 --> 26:13.781
Manny, he's just now getting
back to his old self.

26:13.864 --> 26:17.952
I mean, he went into seclusion
when he lost his family, so.

26:18.035 --> 26:21.372
- So, you're saying I should
just show up at his door?

26:21.455 --> 26:23.335
- I mean, I think that
you taking the initiative

26:23.374 --> 26:25.418
will show him that
he's safe with you.

26:28.045 --> 26:30.423
Yeah, yeah?

26:30.506 --> 26:33.718
- I don't wanna it to make
it seem like I'm chasing him.

26:33.801 --> 26:35.344
- But you aren't, right?

26:35.428 --> 26:37.388
This is different.

26:39.598 --> 26:40.598
- Come on.

26:41.392 --> 26:42.059
- Okay.

26:42.143 --> 26:43.019
- Yes!

26:43.102 --> 26:44.329
I'm gonna text you his address.

26:44.353 --> 26:47.898
Alright and let me
know when you have it.

26:49.025 --> 26:49.734
- Got it.

26:49.817 --> 26:51.068
- Cool.

26:52.069 --> 26:53.404
Alright, let's bless the food.

26:53.696 --> 26:55.507
Heavenly Father we come
to you saying thank you.

26:55.531 --> 26:57.950
Thank you for this day,
thank you for this business

26:58.034 --> 27:00.053
and thank you for this food
that we're about to receive

27:00.077 --> 27:03.122
and thank you that Sheila's
gonna go over to Manny's house.

27:03.205 --> 27:04.205
Amen.

27:09.086 --> 27:10.087
- I hate you.

27:10.379 --> 27:12.673
So hard.

27:16.135 --> 27:19.138
I just wanna be with my family.

27:19.221 --> 27:21.057
You took them!

27:21.140 --> 27:23.309
You took them from me!

27:36.572 --> 27:37.572
I'm coming.

27:44.038 --> 27:45.164
- Jesus.

27:47.500 --> 27:49.043
- What are you doin'?

27:51.462 --> 27:52.462
What are you looking for?

27:52.505 --> 27:53.547
- Nothing.

27:53.631 --> 27:55.633
Where'd you hide her?

27:55.716 --> 27:56.425
Where is she?

27:56.509 --> 27:57.301
- Who?

27:57.385 --> 27:58.385
- In here?

27:59.470 --> 28:01.263
- Who are you talking about?

28:01.347 --> 28:02.765
- How'd it go with Sheila?

28:04.308 --> 28:05.744
- Is that who
you're looking for?

28:05.768 --> 28:06.685
- You got any beer
in the fridge?

28:06.769 --> 28:08.020
- No.

28:08.104 --> 28:08.813
Yeah.

28:08.896 --> 28:09.896
- Yeah ya do.

28:11.065 --> 28:12.066
Jesus, boy.

28:16.112 --> 28:17.232
So, how'd it go with Sheila?

28:17.279 --> 28:18.279
- It went fine.

28:19.240 --> 28:19.949
