out with the Pastor,

28:57.653 --> 29:00.156
now you crying over a
old school that needed

29:00.239 --> 29:02.217
his head bashed in for
putting his hands on that...

29:02.241 --> 29:03.576
- Come on, man, we don't,

29:03.659 --> 29:04.410
we don't do it like that.

29:04.493 --> 29:05.578
- But that's what we do.

29:06.871 --> 29:07.788
What, you put a
pistol in his face,

29:07.872 --> 29:09.039
Catch the Holy Ghost?

29:09.123 --> 29:11.000
You think he's supposed to what?

29:13.377 --> 29:15.629
- If you think that's
how it goes down,

29:15.713 --> 29:17.298
maybe this ain't for me no more.

29:17.381 --> 29:18.549
- Naw, it's for you.

29:18.632 --> 29:20.134
What ain't for you
is that pastor.

29:20.217 --> 29:21.510
You drop him and we get goin'.

29:21.594 --> 29:23.345
- Let me tell you something.

29:23.429 --> 29:25.222
It come down to
that pastor or you,

29:26.307 --> 29:27.558
I'm picking that pastor.

29:32.396 --> 29:33.189
- Alright.

29:33.272 --> 29:35.316
Well, then maybe I
need to go down there

29:35.399 --> 29:39.153
and have a little man-to-man
conversation with that pastor,

29:39.236 --> 29:40.236
put some hands on him.

29:41.780 --> 29:43.073
- Let me tell you something.

29:43.157 --> 29:45.201
You don't go no where near him.

29:46.368 --> 29:48.871
You understand that?

29:48.954 --> 29:50.372
- Yeah, got you.

30:00.424 --> 30:01.717
Where my drink?

30:05.262 --> 30:07.139
What's funny?

30:07.223 --> 30:08.641
What's funny?

30:08.724 --> 30:09.725
- Hey.

30:57.398 --> 30:58.399
- Sheila.

30:58.482 --> 30:59.733
- Hi.

30:59.817 --> 31:01.127
- What are you doing here?

31:01.151 --> 31:02.420
- I was just in
the neighborhood,

31:02.444 --> 31:03.362
thought I might stop by.

31:03.445 --> 31:05.072
- Really?

31:05.155 --> 31:06.657
- Did I catch you at a bad time?

31:08.951 --> 31:09.951
- No.

31:11.579 --> 31:13.205
- Can I come in?

31:13.289 --> 31:14.289
- Absolutely.

31:22.548 --> 31:24.466
Hey let me take that for you.

31:24.550 --> 31:25.593
- Thank you.

31:25.676 --> 31:26.844
- That's so cool.

31:26.927 --> 31:28.238
I appreciate you
coming with food.

31:28.262 --> 31:30.306
- Thank you, I didn't
know you had company.

31:30.389 --> 31:31.389
- Hi Sheila.

31:31.432 --> 31:32.224
What a surprise.

31:32.308 --> 31:33.017
- No, no.

31:33.100 --> 31:34.893
He was just leaving.

31:34.977 --> 31:35.977
- I was?

31:36.020 --> 31:37.020
I thought we were...

31:39.773 --> 31:41.191
That's right.

31:41.275 --> 31:43.193
I have a thing,
it's very important.

31:43.277 --> 31:44.277
- Yeah, that thing.

31:44.320 --> 31:45.237
- I've got to get to a thing.

31:45.321 --> 31:46.548
- That thing, yeah, that
thing we talked about.

31:46.572 --> 31:47.406
Okay.

31:47.489 --> 31:48.240
- Yeah and my beer's finished,

31:48.324 --> 31:49.658
so I mean, it's perfect timing.

31:49.742 --> 31:51.577
- Yeah, got those things to do.

31:51.660 --> 31:54.330
- Alright, well don't do
anything I would do, okay?

31:54.413 --> 31:57.875
- You two, you two are pathetic.

31:59.293 --> 32:01.503
- Got to work on our
non-verbals, obviously.

32:04.381 --> 32:08.218
- I hope you haven't eaten yet.

32:08.302 --> 32:10.971
