32:16.393 --> 32:17.936
- Well, salmon...

32:19.313 --> 32:20.522
- Salmon.

32:20.606 --> 32:22.816
- With a raspberry
chipotle glaze.

32:22.900 --> 32:24.360
- Alright.

32:24.443 --> 32:28.822
- Pan seared squash and
a fully loaded salad.

32:30.157 --> 32:31.157
- Well, well.

32:32.618 --> 32:34.995
Sounds too good to be true.

32:35.079 --> 32:36.455
I'm gonna go change.

32:36.538 --> 32:37.790
Kitchen is all yours.

32:37.873 --> 32:38.873
- Alright.

32:42.044 --> 32:43.712
Excuse me, excuse me.

32:43.796 --> 32:44.876
I'm looking for my husband.

32:44.922 --> 32:45.631
He just...

32:45.714 --> 32:46.423
- Mrs. Thomas?

32:46.507 --> 32:47.299
- Yes, yes, that's me.

32:47.383 --> 32:48.383
- I'm Dr. Freeman.

32:48.425 --> 32:49.134
- How is he?

32:49.218 --> 32:49.927
- Are you here alone?

32:50.010 --> 32:51.804
- Yes, yes, how is he?

