33:03.649 --> 33:04.942
- No.

33:05.025 --> 33:07.319
- The surgery should
take about four hours.

33:07.403 --> 33:08.588
You know, I know
it's gonna be hard,

33:08.612 --> 33:10.572
but try to get some rest.

33:10.656 --> 33:12.256
You know, if you have
anyone who can come

33:12.282 --> 33:15.119
