a good time to call them.

33:15.202 --> 33:16.495
- Thank you, doctor.

33:16.578 --> 33:19.540
- I'll ask Joseph
to come and get you

33:19.623 --> 33:21.500
before we take him to
the operation room.

33:21.583 --> 33:22.876
- Thank you again, doctor.

33:22.960 --> 33:23.711
- He's in good hands.

33:23.794 --> 33:25.045
Okay, okay.

33:42.730 --> 33:43.730
- Pastor.

33:45.482 --> 33:47.443
Can I talk to you for a second?

33:51.447 --> 33:52.447
- Alright.

34:04.543 --> 34:06.962
I see some things never change.

34:10.424 --> 34:12.092
- I need you to do
something for me.

34:15.053 --> 34:16.472
- What is it?

34:16.554 --> 34:18.389
- I need you to cover
me in prayers again.

34:21.726 --> 34:23.228
- What you need, Silk?

34:23.312 --> 34:25.147
- Please, man, just cover
me in prayers again.

34:30.902 --> 34:32.446
I got to tell you something.

34:35.114 --> 34:36.114
- Go ahead.

34:37.951 --> 34:40.454
- I think I killed
this old man today.

34:43.748 --> 34:44.917
- Wait, you did what?

34:45.833 --> 34:51.297
- I mean, this old man was
beating up on his old lady,

34:51.380 --> 34:54.051
so I stepped in,
next thing I know,

34:55.260 --> 34:56.469
he's having a heart attack.

35:01.225 --> 35:04.520
- Do you know, are you
for sure that he's dead?

35:05.604 --> 35:06.939
- Come on man.

35:07.022 --> 35:08.862
I didn't sit around there
to wait and find out.

35:12.236 --> 35:13.362
