37:59.528 --> 38:03.573
- One day, one day
something'll catch up with you.

38:31.643 --> 38:32.728
- What do you,

38:33.687 --> 38:35.105
what do you want?

38:35.188 --> 38:37.190
Your father's in the ICU.

38:37.274 --> 38:38.775
He had a heart
attack last night.

38:41.820 --> 38:42.529
Sandra, you hear me?

38:42.612 --> 38:43.655
- Where are you?

38:43.739 --> 38:45.240
- I'm at Baylor.

38:46.408 --> 38:49.161
- Okay, I'll be there
as soon as I can.

38:58.962 --> 39:00.338
