39:06.344 --> 39:09.389
- Doctors told him about
his drinking and smoking.

39:09.473 --> 39:12.476
- He wasn't drinking and
he hasn't a cigarette

39:12.559 --> 39:13.852
in months now.

39:13.935 --> 39:15.645
You could act a
little more concerned.

39:15.729 --> 39:16.855
- I'm concerned about you.

39:17.647 --> 39:18.857
- That is still your father.

39:18.940 --> 39:20.442
- That is not my father.

39:21.735 --> 39:23.087
If they would have
known what kind of man

39:23.111 --> 39:25.151
they had on that table,
they would have let him die.

39:26.698 --> 39:27.616
- Sandra, dear.

39:27.699 --> 39:28.699
Sandra, I'm so sorry.

39:29.451 --> 39:30.327
Baby, I'm so sorry.

39:30.410 --> 39:32.537
- Let go of my arm.

39:32.621 --> 39:35.165
Let you stand by your
man like you always do.

39:37.501 --> 39:38.293
- Mrs. Thomas?

39:38.376 --> 39:39.169
- Yes.

39:39.252 --> 39:41.213
- The surgery was a success.

39:41.296 --> 39:42.798
He's really strong.

39:42.881 --> 39:44.883
- We've done everything
we can, but what he needs

39:44.966 --> 39:46.885
more than anything
