39:50.305 --> 39:51.598
- Thank you, doctor.

39:51.681 --> 39:52.681
- Of course.

40:27.551 --> 40:31.555
- There is something
about a man in a nice suit.

40:31.638 --> 40:33.682
- Shh, I'll tell you what.

40:33.765 --> 40:37.018
