40:37.102 --> 40:38.854
- This is your uniform, Pastor.

40:38.937 --> 40:42.649
Look, a nice suit
exudes confidence.

40:46.903 --> 40:48.881
- Yeah, but I don't know
if I should spend this much

40:48.905 --> 40:50.866
