40:50.949 --> 40:54.744
- No, you should,
and deservingly so.

40:54.828 --> 40:56.788
Yeah?

40:59.374 --> 41:01.334
- Alright, I'll take it.

41:01.418 --> 41:02.645
- Alright, just hand it
to me when you're done

41:02.669 --> 41:03.545
