41:11.052 --> 41:12.762
Yeah, 'cause, yeah.

41:14.848 --> 41:16.308
- This is real nice.

41:16.391 --> 41:17.100
- Yeah.

41:17.184 --> 41:19.227
- Man, look at that.

41:19.311 --> 41:20.311
These cufflinks.

41:21.938 --> 41:23.607
- Um, thank you?

41:24.441 --> 41:25.442
- No, thank you.

